Path: godot/classes/class_graphframe.rst
Summary: Defines theme properties for customizing the appearance of GraphFrame nodes.

Theme Properties:
* resizer_color (Color): The color of the resizer handle. Default: Color(0.875, 0.875, 0.875, 1).
* panel (StyleBox): The StyleBox for the main panel of the frame.
* panel_selected (StyleBox): The StyleBox for the main panel of the frame when selected.
* titlebar (StyleBox): The StyleBox for the title bar of the frame.
* titlebar_selected (StyleBox): The StyleBox for the title bar of the frame when selected.
