Document: GraphFrame
Path: godot/classes/class_graphframe.rst
Summary: Describes the theme properties available for customizing the appearance of a GraphFrame node.

Theme Property Descriptions
resizer_color (Color): The color modulation applied to the resizer icon. Default: Color(0.875, 0.875, 0.875, 1).
panel (StyleBox): The default StyleBox used for the background of the GraphFrame.
panel_selected (StyleBox): The StyleBox used for the background of the GraphFrame when it is selected.
titlebar (StyleBox): The StyleBox used for the title bar of the GraphFrame.
titlebar_selected (StyleBox): The StyleBox used for the title bar of the GraphFrame when it is selected.